Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:22.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}魔法把声音传递
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我好想歌唱与你
